  "text": "CRM is one of the most important objectives in at least 60% of the projects in the world. The great advances in technology was an important reason for the division of territories in the market, strengthen relationships with customers, and provide adequate information that will help in finding effective methods of dealing with customers. From the perspective of [CITATION_1] , CRM would be realization and understanding in terms of beneficiaries if they have flexibility in the use and implementation.",
